               MOVE    MCPDATA-REC         TO  ADRS-REC
               MOVE    ZERO                TO  FLG-ADRS
           ELSE
               INITIALIZE                      ADRS-REC
               MOVE    1                   TO  FLG-ADRS
           END-IF
      *
           .
       900-ADRS-READ-EXT.
           EXIT.
